about.summary: Provides a convenient interface in 'OpenMx' for building Estabrook's (2015) <doi:10.1037/a0034523> Measurement Model of Derivatives (MMOD).

name: r-mxmmod
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '1.0.1' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-mxmmod
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/mxmmod_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/mxmmod/mxmmod_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: bb0b0fbdf4c4a3f594eccbaf83c557da388654fa333222e353c5fd461a6e6065

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-openmx
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-openmx

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('mxmmod')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('mxmmod')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/khusmann/mxmmod
  license: Apache-2.0
  summary: Provides a convenient interface in 'OpenMx' for building Estabrook's (2015) <doi:10.1037/a0034523>
    Measurement Model of Derivatives (MMOD).
  license_family: APACHE
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - khusmann
